name: Katy B
description: '''Kathleen Anne Brien''' (born 8 May 1989), known professionally as '''Katy B''', is an English singer. She released her debut studio album, ''[[On a Mission (Katy B album)|On a Mission]]'', in 2011, which spawned two top five hits, "[[Katy on a Mission]]" and "[[Lights On (Katy B song)|Lights On]]". In 2014 she released her second studio album, ''[[Little Red (album)|Little Red]]'', which produced her third top five hit, "[[Crying for No Reason]]". Her third studio album, ''[[Honey (Katy B album)|Honey]]'', was released in 2016.
